title: Mason Mitchell wins ARCA finale at Kansas Speedway
text:
Mason Mitchell wins ARCA finale at Kansas Speedway; Grant Enfinger takes season title By ASHLEY DUNKAK Associated Press   10:55   10:55   
Subjects: 
Kansas (527) 

KANSAS CITY, Kansas â€” Mason Mitchell won the ARCA Racing Series season finale Friday night, edging Kyle Weatherman at Kansas Speedway for his second victory of the year. 
Grant Enfinger won the season championship by starting the race, and went on to finish third. He had six victories and 12 top-five finishes this year. 
"The biggest thing this year has been speed," Enfinger said before the race. "I feel we've been competitive everywhere we've gone this season. We've had a chance to win or lead laps every race, it seems."
